{"TopicId":172663,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.12.x] ABookCase Orbital Reference System Updated","CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T11:02:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T11:02:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nForum user \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/151841-zentarul/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022151841\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/151841-zentarul/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@zentarul\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0made this nice little mod at the request of Twitch streamer ABookCase.\u00A0 It hasn\u0027t been updated since KSP 1.2, and I had a request to update it.\u00A0 Original thread is here:\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/131706-12-abookcase-orbital-reference-system-0410/\u0026amp;\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/131706-12-abookcase-orbital-reference-system-0410/\u0026amp;\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EThis is a request from ABookCase who wanted a simple mod that displays altitude of an orbit at a point by hovering the mouse over it.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EDownload:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/abcors/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/abcors/releases\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ESpacedock:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/1756/ABookCase%20Orbital%20Reference%20System%20Updated\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/1756/ABookCase Orbital Reference System Updated\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EGithub:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/abcors\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/abcors\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ELicense: MIT\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nNow available via \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003EMain change is that there is now a Settings page, available\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003E\u00A0in the stock settings page, and no more need for a local config file.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe mouse is not shown in the screenshots, but I\u0027m sure you can imagine it.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KSCpl50.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KSCpl50.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EImgur Gallery:\u00A0\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/K6wiA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/a/K6wiA\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-03-19T11:18:40Z\u0022 title=\u002203/19/2018 11:18  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 19, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by linuxgurugamer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ioresult","CreatedById":117573,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T13:35:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh I missed this one! Thank you LGG!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebs_SY","CreatedById":169510,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T16:57:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLove this mod. IMHO a little underrated. Thanks LGG!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"I3laze","CreatedById":138157,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T18:04:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks For updating.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ar_Taq","CreatedById":113212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T05:36:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBook and I thank you for keeping it going!\u00A0 This mod has always been completely underrated!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-23T12:53:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329678\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521610574\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113212\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ar_Taq\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/21/2018 at 1:36 AM, Ar_Taq said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBook and I thank you for keeping it going!\u00A0 This mod has always been completely underrated!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour welcome.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, to get Book to actually play it again....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"crapstar","CreatedById":161374,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-20T21:56:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this compatible with 1.3.1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-24T18:24:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew release, 0.5.0.5\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nVersion bump for recompile\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUpdated AssemblyVersion.tt with path-independent code\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bpiltz","CreatedById":151083,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-25T07:01:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother one of those mods you didn\u0027t know you needed and then can\u0027t imagine playing the game without.\u00A0 Thanks for keeping the good ones going.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-21T10:54:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew release, 0.5.1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nAdded InstallChecker\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nRebuild for 1.8\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cruesoe","CreatedById":189638,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-21T13:22:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t know I needed this until now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lechu","CreatedById":200130,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-02T16:39:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere do I find the settings page?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansAcker","CreatedById":195534,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-02T17:07:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223876152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604335147\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200130\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lechu\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, Lechu said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere do I find the settings page?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the \u0022Game Difficulty\u0022 settings. There should be a \u0022ABCORS\u0022 tab on the left side:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022fYLKwlcwv5A0N2M-qgwlqGVzP-iRuZqxAkj9B4e1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002273.75\u0022 height=\u0022688\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/fYLKwlcwv5A0N2M-qgwlqGVzP-iRuZqxAkj9B4e1r0mXTIskwLi2DcMDp5qEHuqVUqwhXJeHZoE3uQed33lrxSegagy-Y-6SQNz-De52DjLnovAAhNqpjNHGZRgV_Iq2bqZQheHo\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOld but useful thread:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022138988\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1052544586\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/158325-settings-explained/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-02T10:58:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew releases\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0.5.1.4 (on July 16)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nAdded AssemblyFileVersion\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUpdated version file for 1.12\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n0.5.1.5\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThanks to github user @lampeh for this fix:\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nOnly show popup in map view\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gordon Dry","CreatedById":163177,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-08T17:40:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou forgot to put 0.5.1.5 on Spacedock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-08T21:50:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224052625\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u0